column5: We would like to wish all members and their families a very Happy New Year. May 2017 be a safe and healthy time for us all. Rick and Dianne.
Thank you both and same to you and all others!
Happy New Year to you also npt1
Right back atcha!!! And to everyone else also!!!!!
All the best for 2017 to all.  Went out  all the kids/ grands last night. Today 3 came back for a late lunch!!! Mom's Lasagna and dad's lamb BBQ
